Templates.Name: UK SEPA Payments
Templates.s2cor__Description__c: This template contains all the feed broker, feeds and rules to generate a SEPA Credit Transfer. Payments to suppliers and SEPA Direct Debits to customers. SEPA (Single Euro Payments Area) uses a standard format for payments between companies in most European countries.
